LaTeX letter heads for the Geophysical Institute and the University of
Alaska Fairbanks

It provides the two classes, UAFletter.cls and GIletter.cls, which
only differ in their respective logos. The classes are based on the
ETHbrief package (http://www.sg.ethz.ch/downloads/LaTeX).

To invoke the GIletter:

\documentclass[english]{GIletter}
\usepackage{GI-aschwanden}

and for UAFletter:

\documentclass[english]{UAFletter}
\usepackage{GI-aschwanden}

GI-aschwanden.sty is given for convenience. I recommend you make a
copy, UAF-smith.sty, and edit your personal information there.

Andy Aschwanden, University of Alaska Fairbanks
